  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. COU1 is the validation activity itself — the FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) below required level due to single test condition. Uncertainty quantification was performed via Monte Carlo propagation of material property and geometric tolerances; a screening sensitivity study is described in the UQ report narrative identifying elastic modulus and cross-sectional diameter as influential, but no structured sensitivity analysis object has been linked to this package.",
